{"tid":1032594,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"謝四回歸晏菲路踢元老賽","createTime":"2019-02-22T13:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T18:46:24.000Z","uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d33264d4d6d392dd4a38883dac5df37f95b4a3a2","tid":1032594,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=dd009df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】神奇隊長謝拉特下月回歸晏菲路，代表利物浦出戰元老賽。<br />\n<br />\n現年38歲的謝拉特（Steven Gerrard）目前執教蘇超格拉斯哥流浪，日前證實下月再次現身晏菲路，為利物浦出戰元老賽，對手是意甲勁旅AC米蘭。這場大戰定於3月23日，利物浦名宿包括加歷查、古治、希比亞、丹尼爾艾格和「晏菲路之神」科拿；AC米蘭的26人名單則有卡卡、派路、馬甸尼、卡富、尼斯達、迪達和加度素等。<br />\n<br />\n這戲碼令人聯想到兩軍2005年在歐聯決賽的激戰，利物浦在落後3球情況下追平，並憑互射12碼勝出逆轉捧盃。<br />\n<br />\n謝四於2016年掛靴，踢而優則教，帶領格流以52分在蘇超排名次席，落後些路迪8分。"},{"pid":"bbf7f8889c2a08aac6d86614714cff7ca90849e8","tid":1032594,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"謝拉特又黎黑走利記既英超冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab689ce5b3f632d86fff0d5b15525c483230344a","tid":1032594,"uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bbf7f8889c2a08aac6d86614714cff7ca90849e8","tid":1032594,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"謝拉特又黎黑走利記既英超冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"黑得走嘅話我用肉身餵野生老虎"},{"pid":"6e9a0d56bf01c1d7722d1210081f5539958dd9b0","tid":1032594,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"咪撚再洗腳"},{"pid":"a8758ba89438771fc352c9863eaae32f8c67dabd","tid":1032594,"uid":169208,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnBLx6R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnBLx6R.png&h=99e5f3a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8be87fd76bba4c301340de58682cf48c2ce021bb","tid":1032594,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:38:41.000Z","msg":"果年教青年軍咪即刻賴野"},{"pid":"5cd855fc081d9c6f1407c635cfe2367ace077c84","tid":1032594,"uid":229906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:46:24.000Z","msg":"米蘭個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}